The '''''Prodigal''''' was a modified [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300 light freighter]] assigned to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Harrier Infiltration Team]]. It was under the command of Harrier team leader [[Fable Astin/Legends|Fable Astin]].<ref name="Uhl Eharl Khoehng">{{JournalCite|8|Uhl Eharl Khoehng (short story)}}</ref>

